==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Insulting
<hw>In*sult"ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Containing, or characterized
by, insult or abuse; tending to insult or affront; <as>as,
<ex>insulting</ex> language, treatment, etc.</as></def> --
<wordforms><wf>In*sult"ing*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms></p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Insolent; impertinent; saucy; rude; abusive;
contemptuous. See <er>Insolent</er>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Insultment</ent>⟦br⟧
